Read the INSTALL file for information on how to get Dufie
built, configured, and running properly.
_________________________________________________________

Dufie: The Disk Usage Front [i] End.

Dufie is a front end for the linux 'du' command (shipped
with the fileutils package). It provides a graphical user
interface for how much space directories and their
contents are taking up on your hard drive(s).
